    Elements" adaptive="false" timeDependent="false">
    <itemBody>
        <p>Look at the following large table. A system fails if the header and footer are not
            visible. Systems should display both header and footer even if the body of the table
            cannot be displayed completely on the screen, page etc. Note that this example does not
            validate against v2.0 of the QTI schema due to a bug in that specification.</p>
